---

This product includes GeoLite data created by DB-IP, available from
https://db-ip.com, embedded as:

  assets/dbip-country-lite.mmdb
    IP geolocation database used for country lookups during report enrichment.

That file is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International
License (CC BY 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

---

This project is based on parsedmarc (https://github.com/domainaware/parsedmarc)
by Domain Aware, licensed under the Apache License 2.0.

The following file was taken directly from the parsedmarc project:

  assets/base_reverse_dns_map.csv
    A map of reverse DNS base domains to sender names and types (ESPs, ISPs,
    CDNs). Used for sender identification during report enrichment.

That file is subject to the Apache License 2.0 under which parsedmarc is
distributed. The Apache License 2.0 applies to that file only; all other
files in this repository are MIT licensed as stated above.

A copy of the Apache License 2.0 is available at:
